protein.specific_function: Protein phosphatase involved in the inactivation of MAP kinases. Has a specificity for the MAPK11/MAPK12/MAPK13/MAPK14 subfamily.

go_class.description: hydrolase activity, acting on ester bonds
negative regulation of JUN kinase activity
negative regulation of respiratory burst involved in inflammatory response
